message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. It comes with a range of advanced features that can significantly enhance your experience. Considering its quality and functionality, I believe it would be a valuable addition to your collection. For this exceptional product, I am offering it at $15000. I am confident it will exceed your expectations and provide substantial value to you.
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $12000. I believe it's a bit above my budget, but I'm willing to make a compromise.
